  <Properties />
  <Nodes>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement1" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[The example]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement1"><![CDATA[<p>Open a ContextMenu for the DataGridView and select a menu item for the following actions:<br />a) Add Row - open new form to enter data about new user;<br />b) Modify Row - open new form to change user data for each selected rows;<br />c) Delete Row - delete all selected row.<br />All actions are executed on the DataSet that is DataSource for the DataGridView.</p>]]></Paragraph>
  </Nodes>
</Data>
